{"tid":1024650,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"食屎啦香港人，竟然為南亞護航","createTime":"2019-02-16T17:22:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-17T02:05:18.000Z","uid":137017,"like":13,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"a0d89958c280b13c0207913ea20467e5c16fc3d5","tid":1024650,"uid":137017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T17:22:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/h65STN6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fh65STN6.png&h=b8e04147&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n究竟有幾低賤先會讚揚啲狗？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n讚揚一班搞亂香港嘅契弟，踩香港人踩到上心口，咁樣都可以讚佢哋，你地個腦根本就係裝屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n講搶資源佢哋一D都唔少、講犯罪率你自己睇吓啲風化案、搶劫案、謀殺案&hellip;佢哋佔咗幾多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好心唔好咁弱智啦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港嘅女仔，請自重"},{"pid":"9d312d9af641ff8b1d5dc92de83f1cca6853e739","tid":1024650,"uid":90820,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T17:27:05.000Z","msg":"識欣賞蝻嘅知音人<br />\n希望男嘅早日爆菊<br />\n女嘅早日畀蝻輪大米<br />\n等佢哋同啲蝻做深入文化交流<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea54bf0705791daa9d393a6f1fab300527cb7b19","tid":1024650,"uid":90820,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T17:27:45.000Z","msg":"講蝻post必提<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">張超雄仆街死</span></span>"},{"pid":"ea8503855d671a510531245120627e4e53d4ea15","tid":1024650,"uid":198583,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T17:43:42.000Z","msg":"又歧視人<br />\n<br />\n學人講liberty democracy <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"202f012836fae502a6a6a36e8f85959f1d1c2c8b","tid":1024650,"uid":41508,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T17:45:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e9b2a8521760405c9e4a522a22b0f3c2830e8278","tid":1024650,"uid":73473,"lik